    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems like a lot of theory vs the actual reality for small shops right now. i mean, can these new jobs really make up for the fact that local manufacturers might actually have to shut down because they cant afford the compliance? it feels like a massive gamble with people's livelihoods.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
